@startuml fecgov_fec-eregs

actor User
actor Developer

cloud "Cloud Foundry" {
  node "FEC eRegs Application" {
    [Django Web App]
    [regulations-site]
    [regulations-core]
    [regulations-parser]
    [eregs_extensions]
  }
  database "PostgreSQL" {
    [Regulations Data]
  }
  database "ElasticSearch" {
    [Search Index]
  }
}

node "External Services" {
  [FEC CMS]
  [FEC API]
}

User -> [Django Web App] : Access regulations
Developer -> [Cloud Foundry] : Deploy (tasks.py)

[Django Web App] --> [regulations-site] : Extends
[Django Web App] --> [regulations-core] : Uses
[Django Web App] --> [regulations-parser] : Uses
[Django Web App] --> [eregs_extensions] : Customizes

[regulations-core] --> [Regulations Data] : Read/Write
[regulations-parser] --> [Regulations Data] : Parse and Load

[Django Web App] --> [Search Index] : Query
[regulations-parser] --> [Search Index] : Index

[Django Web App] --> [FEC CMS] : Fetch content
[Django Web App] --> [FEC API] : Fetch data

@enduml